{"tid":2405083,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"盆菜苦主大聯盟","createTime":"2021-02-12T06:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T09:43:07.000Z","uid":89388,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5905d35b136ad60ebf49bab1a13a86980fc0419a","tid":2405083,"uid":89388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:14:54.000Z","msg":"本身冇諗過開post<br />\n留左言係佢live段片 點知唔夠一個鐘成條片del左 又話九點後一律退款<br />\n如果佢唔係del post 我唔會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有好多苦主post左相 同埋要求退款既留言都冇哂<br />\n個個都嬲到核爆<br />\n<br />\n講返少少背景 個送貨就遲左大概一個鐘九個字<br />\n打哂兩邊都冇人聽<br />\n屋企人已經躁到一個點<br />\n<br />\n盤入要有3隻鵝掌 一舊鴨胸 三舊腩肉 完全無髮菜蠔豉<br />\n啲豬手無味仲要全部都係趾骨<br />\n啲蝦無挑腸 成條黑猛猛<br />\n汁少又無味 聞落d料有酸味 咬落都有d酸性<br />\n<br />\n魚蛋冇數過實際數過 <br />\n目測成個盤底都係 應該20粒樓上<br />\nd蛙蛙菜係又硬又生 未熟就鋪係個底到<br />\n<br />\n白蘿蔔得三四粒 切到魚蛋咁細 但硬身起渣<br />\n仲有陣苦澀味<br />\n<br />\n哈蝦蝦 訂個個係6人份量🙃4個人食仲要淥麵<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"pink\"><span class=\"x-large\">PS佢一隻鵝掌係預你兩個人用口一齊損 好sweet</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n隻鮑魚食落仲衰過假鮑片陣味<br />\n酸酸縮縮咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都唔知係d冬菇 定豬皮扮花膠縮左<br />\n總之就比屋企人剷到上天花板<br />\n個盆又細 大過隻手掌少少<br />\n<br />\n當佢地問個價錢 口震震答$288 算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">下面係我揾返有部份苦主既投訴<br />\n<br />\n你地有都可以幫手放上黎 廢時又比佢delete留言</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cu3JQwe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCu3JQwe.jpg&h=c2f2e14f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\"><span class=\"xx-large\">一手揸得哂 冇屈佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TjD2mCV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjD2mCV.jpg&h=4c997837&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9ZfTthW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9ZfTthW.jpg&h=2b19c5b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AxoxJRh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAxoxJRh.jpg&h=a1ea08ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DZiE8hX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDZiE8hX.jpg&h=36c67752&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YsMGCbi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYsMGCbi.jpg&h=42de842c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7xU1Cbj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7xU1Cbj.jpg&h=705de577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KSP5jpF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKSP5jpF.jpg&h=53ad022f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等開年"},{"pid":"c4f7cf000ac04f1a3674cf24ad6f97966761952d","tid":2405083,"uid":53375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T0